{"id":267629,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-深圳ngo小小草工友家园-诉深圳宝安公安/","date":"2012-12-10T18:31:37Z","modified":"2012-12-10T18:31:37Z","title":"维权网 | 深圳NGO“小小草工友家园” 诉深圳宝安公安分局行政不作为案12月10日开庭（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a>（维权网信息员赵小明报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日星期一，深圳劳工</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">NGO</span><span>“小小草工友家园”</span> <span>诉讼深圳市公安局宝安分局行政不作为一案开庭。此案缘由是：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span><span>余人强行闯进小小草良心活动室，将东西扔出门外并锁死门。“小小草”工作人员及时报警但警察姗姗来迟，未能阻止暴力事件的发生。为此，小小草起诉了深圳市公安局宝安分局行政不作为，此案于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>公开审理，地点在宝安区人民法院三楼九庭。</span>  </p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>“小小草”义工和志愿者共</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>余人参与旁听，</span><span>庭审进行了</span><span>两个小时后</span><span>结束。庭审后他们在宝安法院门口合影，并拉起了“社会要和谐，公安要给力”的横幅。他们希望宝安区人民法院随后能够做出公正的判决。</span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Q-N4Td7Ywes/UMYPISUdDyI/AAAAAAAAV7w/Dgm-xNdBO60/s1600/a1aa197fjw1dzormkcmenj.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Q-N4Td7Ywes/UMYPISUdDyI/AAAAAAAAV7w/Dgm-xNdBO60/s400/a1aa197fjw1dzormkcmenj.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-6805483512064886560?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4